{
  "text": "We recall the notion of diagram twisting as defined in [CITATION_1] . Note that the operations we describe here are only a subset of the operations defined in [CITATION_2] , but that they coincide when we restrict our attention to skew-angled Coxeter groups.",
  "correct_citation": {
